&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h2&gt;About Hightouch&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hightouch is an Agentic Marketing Platform powered by the industry-leading Composable CDP. With complete brand context, customer data, and performance history in one place, every marketer finally has the power to build and ship end-to-end campaigns themselves. Teams move faster, stay on brand, and get AI marketing that actually works.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Founded in 2019 and headquartered in San Francisco, Hightouch enables marketing teams to analyze performance, brainstorm ideas, and generate creative at a speed and quality that wasn&#39;t previously possible.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Named a Leader in the 2026 Gartner® Magic Quadrant™ for Customer Data Platforms, Hightouch is trusted by leading enterprises like Domino&#39;s, Spotify, Aritzia, Cars.com, Ramp, and PetSmart.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Hightouch, our mission is to help our customers leverage data and AI to grow their businesses. The team is ambitious, impact-driven, efficient — and we believe humility, kindness, and compassion are essential to our success. If you&#39;re energized by velocity, obsessed with raising the bar, and want to build alongside people who care deeply about each other and our customers, we&#39;d love to meet you.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;About The Role&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hightouch is looking for a Mid-Market Account Executive to join the founding Ad Studio sales team. Ad Studio is one of our newest products and lets performance marketing teams build, edit, and launch on-brand ads at scale using AI, all backed by first-party data. This is a ground-floor opportunity to help define how we bring it to market.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll be one of the first AEs dedicated to Ad Studio, which means you&#39;ll have real influence over the sales motion, the ICP, and how we position the product with customers. You&#39;re not inheriting a playbook, you&#39;re writing it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The buyers you&#39;ll sell to are performance marketers, paid social and paid search leads, creative strategists, and growth teams at mid-market companies who are constantly battling creative fatigue, slow production cycles, and rising CPMs. You&#39;ll help them see how Ad Studio changes that equation. Adtech or martech sales experience is a real advantage here. If you&#39;ve sold into performance marketing teams before, you know exactly what keeps them up at night and you&#39;ll hit the ground running.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;These are consultative, strategic deals where you&#39;re not just demoing a tool. You&#39;re helping teams rethink how they produce and launch creative.&lt;/p&gt;
