&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;2+ years in a full cycle sales role. We care less about years of experience and more about the impact and results of your work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Excitement about being part of a founding team and comfort with the ambiguity that comes with it&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Background in adtech, martech, creative tools, or selling to performance marketing buyers is a strong plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Strong discovery and interpersonal skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Intellectual curiosity, high ambition, and humility&lt;/li&gt;
