&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re changing that. Hightouch&#39;s Agentic Marketing Platform is the system enterprise marketers are using to plan, generate, and ship lifecycle campaigns with their data, their guidelines, and their voice. Our customers include Domino&#39;s, Chime, Spotify, Ramp, Whoop, and Grammarly. They are not going to settle for slop, and neither are we.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We&#39;re hiring an AI Creative Designer&lt;/strong&gt; to be the human who proves what&#39;s possible. You&#39;ll collaborate alongside our Solutions Engineering team on enterprise customer calls, translate brand guidelines into agentic workflows that actually produce on-brand email and lifecycle creative, and ship the work that makes the case. You will be the most influential creative voice in the room, both for our customers and for our product.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will define how the most recognizable brands in the world build email with AI, and you will watch the work you direct ship to millions of inboxes.&lt;/p&gt;
