&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Multi-tenant&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;isolation&lt;/strong&gt; on a system running ~1M data syncs per day and ingesting 100K+ events/sec&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sub-tenant access control&lt;/strong&gt; - for multi-team and multi-brand use cases, requiring differentiated access to configuration and data&lt;/li&gt;
