&lt;p&gt;Hightouch is at the forefront of the &lt;strong&gt;Data Activation&lt;/strong&gt; movement, empowering businesses to leverage their data warehouses as the source of truth for all their operational needs. Our customer base is rapidly expanding, and you will be a critical leader on the front lines, ensuring that the most innovative companies become passionate, lifelong Hightouch customers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Solutions Engineers are instrumental in ensuring customers&#39; initial experiences with Hightouch&#39;s platform are seamless, leading to successful and enduring partnerships. They collaborate closely with Account Executives (AEs) to guide prospective customers through the pre-sales journey, delivering customized demonstrations and proofs-of-concept (POCs) that culminate in a &quot;Product Yes.&quot; Solutions Engineers are relentlessly curious about customer needs and pain points, leveraging their expert Hightouch product knowledge and deep technical understanding of data warehousing, ETL/ELT, and API integrations to design optimal solutions. Solutions Engineers are adept at building relationships, excel at project management, and are effective leaders who inspire and develop their teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You Will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead, mentor, and grow a team of Solutions Engineers fostering a collaborative, high-performing, and customer-centric environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner strategically with Hightouch AEs throughout the customer journey, delivering tailored demonstrations and customer POCs based on agreed-upon requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop deep technical domain expertise in &lt;strong&gt;Data Activation, CDP, data warehousing (e.g., Snowflake, BigQuery, Databricks), and integration platforms&lt;/strong&gt;, across various industries including financial services, retail, SaaS, and similar enterprises.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be accountable for the exceptional customer experience during the new revenue pilot and closing phases.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage with customers daily to deeply understand their data activation needs and architect elegant solutions that leverage the Hightouch platform to its fullest potential.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, develop, and maintain best-in-class playbooks, demo environments, and other tools to ensure successful and efficient POCs and technical validations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate effectively with AEs and Product Managers to identify and champion customer-specific feature requests and product enhancements.&lt;/li&gt;
